### CCR-013 RBAC + BS-08-04 GER-04 — API Gate
###
### 검증:
### - Operator가 mutation 엔드포인트 호출 → 403 Forbidden
### - Viewer는 조회조차 제한
### - Admin은 모든 엔드포인트 허용
### - 에러 body: AUTH_ROLE_DENIED

@host = http://localhost:18001
@admin_token = {{$dotenv ADMIN_JWT}}
@operator_token = {{$dotenv OPERATOR_JWT}}
@viewer_token = {{$dotenv VIEWER_JWT}}

### 23.1 Operator POST /skins → 403 (GER-01, GER-04)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/skins
Authorization: Bearer {{operator_token}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary

------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test.gfskin"
Content-Type: application/zip

< ./fixtures/wsop-2026-test.gfskin
------WebKitFormBoundary--

# 예상: 403 Forbidden
# {
#   "error": "AUTH_ROLE_DENIED",
#   "message": "이 작업은 Admin 권한이 필요합니다.",
#   "required_role": "Admin",
#   "current_role": "Operator"
# }

### 23.2 Operator PATCH /skins/{id}/metadata → 403
PATCH {{host}}/api/v1/skins/sk_01HVQK-test/metadata
Authorization: Bearer {{operator_token}}
If-Match: W/"3-etag"
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}
Content-Type: application/merge-patch+json

{ "skin_name": "operator-attempt" }

# 예상: 403 Forbidden

### 23.3 Operator PUT /skins/{id}/activate → 403
PUT {{host}}/api/v1/skins/sk_01HVQK-test/activate
Authorization: Bearer {{operator_token}}
If-Match: W/"3-etag"
X-Game-State: IDLE
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}

# 예상: 403 Forbidden

### 23.4 Operator GET /skins → 200 (조회는 허용)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/skins?limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{operator_token}}

# 예상: 200 OK

### 23.5 Operator GET /skins/{id}/metadata → 200 (조회는 허용)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/skins/sk_01HVQK-test/metadata
Authorization: Bearer {{operator_token}}

# 예상: 200 OK + ETag 헤더

### 23.6 Viewer GET /skins → 403 (GER-03 탭 접근 차단)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/skins?limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{viewer_token}}

# 예상: 403 Forbidden
# { "error": "AUTH_ROLE_DENIED", "required_role": "Operator" }

### 23.7 Admin — 전체 CRUD 허용
POST {{host}}/api/v1/skins
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary

------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test.gfskin"
Content-Type: application/zip

< ./fixtures/wsop-2026-test.gfskin
------WebKitFormBoundary--

# 예상: 201 Created

### 23.8 CC 서비스 계정 GET /skins/{id} → 200 (.gfskin 다운로드 허용)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/skins/sk_01HVQK-test
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv CC_SERVICE_JWT}}
Accept: application/octet-stream

# 예상: 200 OK (CC가 skin_updated 이벤트 수신 후 다운로드)

### 23.9 CC 서비스 계정 POST /skins → 403
POST {{host}}/api/v1/skins
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv CC_SERVICE_JWT}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary

------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="cc-attempt.gfskin"
Content-Type: application/zip

< ./fixtures/wsop-2026-test.gfskin
------WebKitFormBoundary--

# 예상: 403 Forbidden (CC는 read-only)
